<i>noun</i>: 상 [상], 사별 [사ː별] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>상 [상]</dt><br>
<dd>bereavement; death in the family</dd><br>
<dd>가족이 죽는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A family member's death.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사별 [사ː별]</dt><br>
<dd>bereavement; separation by death</dd><br>
<dd>가족 구성원 중 한 쪽이 먼저 죽어서 헤어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The feeling of separation resulting from the death of a family member</dd><br>
</li>
